{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Peak envelope generator\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Generates envelope based on audio item peaks. You can think of it as an offline audio source parameter baker.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Requires ReaImGui, but will prompt you to install it and provide ReaPack repo, if you don't already have it.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Contains built-in documentation in UI.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Only works with FX envelopes at the moment\par}
}

